          "_anchor": "ingredients",
          "_cid": "vpfxYdru5Q",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".counter-container": {
              "ol": {
                "margin-bottom": "0",
                "li": {
                  "margin-bottom": "1rem"
                },
                "& when (@stylizedCounters)": {
                  "counter-reset": "myCounter",
                  "li": {
                    "list-style": "none",
                    "padding-left": "1rem",
                    "position": "relative",
                    "&:before": {
                      "position": "absolute",
                      "left": "-40px",
                      "margin-top": "5px",
                      "counter-increment": "myCounter",
                      "content": "counter(myCounter)",
                      "line-height": "40px",
                      "transition": "all .2s",
                      "color": "contrast(@iconColor)",
                      "background": "@iconColor",
                      "width": "40px",
                      "height": "40px",
                      "border-radius": "50%",
                      "display": "flex",
                      "align-items": "center",
                      "justify-content": "center",
                      "& when (@squareCounters)": {
                        "border-radius": "0"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "_name": "content9",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content9\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"11\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Stylized Counters\" name=\"stylizedCounters\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Square Counters\" name=\"squareCounters\" condition=\"stylizedCounters\">\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#2e7a3d\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"counter-container col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">JellyFil brings together a carefully selected blend of amino acids, botanical extracts, vitamins, and minerals that support men's vitality, daily energy, stamina, circulation, and overall men's wellness. Each ingredient has a specific role in helping adult men maintain an active lifestyle and consistent performance.</h4>\n                <div class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                    <ol>\n                        <li><b>L-Arginine – </b>L-Arginine is an amino acid that helps support the body's natural production of nitric oxide, which plays a role in healthy blood circulation. It also supports physical performance, endurance, and overall male vitality as part of an active lifestyle.</li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">L-Citrulline – </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">L-Citrulline helps the body maintain healthy nitric oxide levels, supporting normal circulation and muscle performance. It also contributes to daily stamina and helps promote sustained energy during regular physical activity.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Panax Ginseng – </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Panax Ginseng is a traditional botanical known for supporting energy, focus, and endurance. It helps the body adapt to everyday stress while encouraging overall vitality and consistent daily performance.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Maca Root Extract – </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Maca Root is widely used to support men's wellness, natural energy, and physical stamina. It also helps maintain daily motivation and supports an active lifestyle.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Tribulus Terrestris – </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Tribulus Terrestris is commonly included in men's wellness supplements to support physical endurance, vitality, and overall well-being. It complements regular exercise and healthy daily habits.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Zinc – </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Zinc is an essential mineral that supports normal immune function, reproductive health, and healthy hormone activity. It also contributes to overall wellness and everyday nutritional support.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Vitamin B6 – </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Vitamin B6 helps the body convert food into energy while supporting normal nervous system function. It also helps reduce feelings of tiredness when consumed as part of a balanced diet.</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Vitamin B12 – </b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Vitamin B12 supports normal energy production, healthy nerve function, and red blood cell formation. It plays an important role in maintaining everyday vitality and overall health.</span></li></ol>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vpfzQEuAzX",
